channel.title: Rum0's Icon Set :O
channel.description:
Well i thought that this should be the right place to post this. If it isn't please move it to the correct spot.
You can download the icons [url=http://www.rscape.nationvoice.com/forum/uploads/Icons.zip]HERE[/url]
Small Example:
[img]http://www.rscape.nationvoice.com/site/icons.png[/img]
To get these to work please unzip them into any folder you want, then simply right click the file you want to change and find the change icon thing browse to the unzipped folder you put the icons in and find the icon you want o_o
I put these together from all the icons i have collected over a long period of time i was bored so i thought i would release this.
sorry about that file that says thumbs it was random it does nothing -.o
